      <h2>Leader</h2>
      <p>In the past, I believed that as a teacher, leaders would tell me what was best for me and what I needed to know. As I began to serve on committees like Building Leadership Team and the Interdisciplinary Team, I realized I had a lot to offer. I began presenting at local conferences and organizing teacher meet ups. My leadership as a teacher has led to opportunities that allow me to advocate for students and teachers.</p>
      <ul>
