    <div class="dual__content">
      <h2>Citizen</h2>
      <p>It is my passion to empower kids and motivate them to take ownership in their learning. My students have connected with classrooms all over the world through Skype and Flipgrid. We have participated in Global Read Aloud and Mystery Skype. Using Project Based Learning, Skype has become a necessity to connect with authors, local businesses, scientists, and inventors. I am committed to raising responsible digital citizens. In my classroom, we used Nearpod lessons supported by Common Sense Media to teach digital citizenship, along with Google's Be Internet Awesome resources.</p>
